{"tid":1451612,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T19:39:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T23:23:14.000Z","uid":294904,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"de4f5226d40a236ead386f63741c19ab8f52a26b","tid":1451612,"uid":294904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:39:42.000Z","msg":"標題：「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\nTG群組，不停轉發出去，勢要討回雙眼，嬲到火屎呀<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n不沖禁區，不沖跑道<br />\n不沖禁區，不沖跑道<br />\n不沖禁區，不沖跑道<br />\n百萬人入機場，機場自然停<br />\n百萬人入機場，機場自然停<br />\n百萬人入機場，機場自然停<br />\n<br />\n大群好多人入緊：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=926QiOG7cNu1sWdYPFF%2FaNLD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=67dbe495\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n睇消息去實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=926QiOG7cNu1sWdYPFF%2FaNLD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=bce009d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"0c334607f74b73af972ca075b08d1439e5d493aa","tid":1451612,"uid":45613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:44:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">612<br />\n721<br />\n811</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">8.12 入機場 不沖禁區同跑道</span>"},{"pid":"7badd5b00e6cc326dbac4bbd6f55543350944784","tid":1451612,"uid":283109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:51:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">機場文宣整合post</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1450351\" data-auto-link target=